  "title": "Driver (Class 3)",
  "description": "<p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS:</strong></p><ol><li>Class 3 driving license </li><li>Ability to work well with a team, hardworking, good attitude and committed to work.</li><li>Organized, independent and initiative and processed good navigation skill.</li><li>Experienace in construction field preferred.</li></ol><p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION:</strong></p><ol><li>Shuttering of material within project zone.</li><li>Transporting workers to & fro dormitory and within site.</li><li><strong>No carrying of material required</strong></li></ol><p><strong>WORKING HOURS:</strong></p><ol><li>5.5 days work week</li><li>Working Hours: 8am-6pm (Mon-Fri), 8am-12noon (Sat).</li><li>Overtimes fees applies after official working hours.</li><li><strong>Vehicle cannot drive home</strong>.</li></ol>",
